<br>
The BoardLurker's guide to Hotkeys.<br>
<br>
Raids:<br>
1.  All hotkeys regardless of function should have the same  format.  If everyone on a raid did this it would be SO much less confusing than trying and pick out important information from the snappy joke lines that get boring after the 3rd tap of the button.<br>
<br>
i.e.<br>
<br>
Heal hotkey<br>
/sit off<br>
/ooc =====[ Greater Healing %T]=====<br>
/cast 4<br>
/say God damn fizzles!<br>
<br>
Incoming hotkey<br>
/shout =====[ Incoming %T ]=====<br>
/attack on<br>
<br>
Assist hotkey<br>
/sit off<br>
/assist Main_Assist_01<br>
/con<br>
<br>
I'm of the mind that assist key's shouldn't have a message attached to them.  Just adds extra battle spam.<br>
<br>
None-raids<br>
<br>
Free-for-all!  Do what ya want here...<br>
