<br>
Taunt<br>
<br>
Disarm<br>
<br>
Bag inventory slot (has my shield and bow in it)<br>
<br>
range inventory slot (so i can switch between bow and idol)<br>
<br>
range attack<br>
<br>
secondary melee inventory slot (so I can swap shield in and out of off hand for ghetto bashing on caster mobs)<br>
